    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Most activities can be left or ended independently by any participant.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "For example, a game being played together or a TV show being watched together",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "doesn’t depend on a particular participant to be able to continue for everyone else.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Some activities, though, might depend on the initiator’s presence in the activity",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "for it to continue.  For example, the initiator might be sharing a photo that",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "belongs to them, or a file from their device.  Setting ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.GroupActivities/documentation/GroupActivities/GroupActivityMetadata/lifetimePolicy-swift.property",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.GroupActivities/documentation/GroupActivities/GroupActivityMetadata/LifetimePolicy-swift.struct/endsWhenInitiatorLeaves",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " in these cases would ensure that",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the activity ends when the initiator leaves.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
